- `keyValuePair.Key` → `keyValuePair.Name` (for JsonProperty)
- `keyValuePair.Value` → `keyValuePair.Value` (same)

And in the inner loop:
- `element.EnumerateObject()` - element is `Dictionary<string, JsonElement>` values → now `JsonElement`, so `.EnumerateObject()` works
- The iteratees also have `.Key`/`.Name` difference

