Actually, looking at the original more carefully, the loop variable names used `.Key` for Dictionary and would need `.Name` for JsonProperty. But actually looking at the original code at lines 53-77, the variable `armProfile` was `Dictionary<string, JsonElement>` and the loop did `foreach (var keyValuePair in armProfile)` using `keyValuePair.Key`. With `JsonElement`, the enumeration uses `.Name` instead of `.Key`.

But wait - lines 56-76 actually already use the right pattern since the inner elements were already `JsonElement` (the value type of the Dictionary). Let me look more carefully:

```csharp
